The evidence with the title 'Chancellor George Osborne's summer budget 2015 speech - gov.uk ' says Jul 8, 2015  ... The OBR forecast that under the current economic conditions , almost a million more jobs will be created over the next five years . Our ambition is to go further, and create 2 million more jobs on the road to full employment . To help achieve that progressive goal , we set out today how we will make work pay. 
